WEBVTT

00:06:30.833 --> 00:06:34.476
It began this slow journey

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:36.792
across calm waters,

00:06:37.458 --> 00:06:40.875
this gentle rolling to the shore.

00:06:43.125 --> 00:06:47.125
Transferring his weight
from left to right and back again,

00:06:48.375 --> 00:06:51.208
Jim became the waves.

00:06:53.750 --> 00:06:57.917
His grace and his strength
just took our breath away.

00:06:59.042 --> 00:07:01.351
For 20 minutes,